headline: State Street Launches MENA Regional Headquarters in Riyadh
summary: RIYADH, Saudi Arabia, October 27, 2025--State Street Corporation (NYSE: STT) today announced the official launch of its Middle East and North Africa Regional Headquarters (RHQ) in Riyadh, Kingdom of Saudi Arabia, following approval from the Ministry of Investment Saudi Arabia (MISA).
